Uses of Package
lanej.schedulingsystem.model

Packages that use lanej.schedulingsystem.model
Package
Description
lanej.schedulingsystem
The main package for the Scheduling System application.
lanej.schedulingsystem.controller
Provides the controller classes for managing the user interface and handling user interactions in the Scheduling System application.
lanej.schedulingsystem.dao
This package contains Data Access Objects (DAO) classes for the scheduling system.
lanej.schedulingsystem.helper
Provides utility classes to assist and support the main functionalities of the scheduling system.
lanej.schedulingsystem.model
Provides the model classes that represent the core business entities of the scheduling system.
